      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena$<BR>My parents were killed by the Dragon Followers because they betrayed them, but no one knows why they betrayed. Maybe they realized how evil the Dragon Followers were and tried to fight for justice.<BR>Maybe... all I want is to find out is if my parents are worth my effort to seek revenge for them.</html>]]></talk_question>
